parameters:
\ncHey, hey, did you watch today's video of Levantia? I was
actually there today.
\nc<Female 2>Eh, really!? Did you see the real thing? How was it?

\ncIt was amazing~! She was shining so brightly and moving
around so energetically.

\ncI thought it was all edited, but the real thing is 500 times
more precious than the video...
\nc<>(...What should I do? It's really itchy...)

\nc<>(But recently, I've been getting asked about my story a
lot.)

\nc<>Thanks to the support of many citizens, we were able to win
even in the second round.
\nc<>(...Maybe I should try doing an ego search.)
\nc<>Oh, there are a lot more than I thought...
\nc<>Could it be that I'm quite popular?

\nc<>Let's see... Their appearance when they appear is cool,
Their courage to confront villains head-on is amazing...
Hmmm, I see.

\nc<>I am more active than other magical girls.
Perhaps
it's because I am an adult and used to fighting.

\nc<>The line of thighs sticking out from the suit is sexy.
What are you saying!?
\nc<>Seriously... Ah, there are people who remember the old me.

\nc<>I got scolded for smoking, or That child has grown so
much.
\nc<>What were you looking at? You had a big grin on your face.
\nc<>Yes! They seemed really happy, you know?
\nc<>It was like Candy when they were watching cat videos.
\nc<>It definitely seems like they would be grinning...

\nc<>(By the way, the reason I started being a magical girl was
because I was happy to be praised by everyone.)

\nc<>Since I became distant from my friends, it's not just that
anymore.
\nc<>I haven't felt like this in a long time...
\nc<>So in the end, what were you looking at?

\nc<>I know. Reina said that when they're looking at naughty
things, I should pretend not to know.
\nc<>What kind of things are they whispering to that child?!

\nc<>Anyway, stop saying stupid things. I'll buy you ice cream,
so let's go to the hideout and eat it.
\nc<>I obtained the memory K1: My First Ego Search.
